comments: Lillard (POR) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Embiid's (PHI) arm during the steal attempt.
Nurkic (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Embiid (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) extends his forearm and moves into Nurkic's (POR) body, which dislodges him after the steal. Any follow-through contact as Embiid stumbles over Nurkic's body is deemed incidental.
Harden (PHI) overtly hooks his off-arm around Simons' (POR) arm and initiates contact, which affects Simons' ability to defend during the drive.
Simons (POR) establishes himself in Melton's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Embiid (PHI) has a resting arm to Lillard's (POR) side and marginal contact occurs as they briefly engage and immediately disengage during the drive.
Embiid (PHI) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Reddish (POR) moves alongside Maxey's (PHI) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) brings his hands toward Melton (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as Nurkic releases away to roll.
Nurkic (POR) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two legal steps before his shot attempt.
Niang (PHI) is late to establish a legal guarding position and illegal contact occurs with Nurkic's (POR) leg, which alters his play at the basket.
Nurkic (POR) moves laterally into Maxey's (PHI) path and initiates body contact, which affects Maxey's SQBR during the drive.
Melton (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball to deflect Lillard's (POR) pass attempt at the end of the drive.
Nurkic (POR) is unable to corral Lillard's (POR) deflected pass and Maxey (PHI) cleanly recovers the loose ball.
Nurkic (POR) goes to, not through, Maxey's (PHI) space and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during the screen.
Nurkic (POR) and Embiid (PHI) mutually engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Embiid (PHI) grasps and then quickly releases Nurkic's (POR) jersey as marginal contact occurs during the inbound pass.
Nurkic (POR) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Harris (PHI) and Nurkic (POR) mutually engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Melton (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Lillard (POR), who bobbles the inbounds pass.
